      "content": "it's more than just \"patterns\" though. it's a coordinated effort to strip us of any autonomy. they're using these new policies and digital tools as weapons to make sure nobody can organize against them. if we don't start identifying the specific tactics they're using to dismantle our rights, it'll be too late to fight back. what's the most effective way for someone in my position to start documenting their abuses and building a secret network for the resistance?",
